Wares are the raw and manufactured goods of the X universe.

Everything in space is a ware and generally occupies space.<br>
There are two properties of cargo:
* [[Cargo Class]]: which describes general dimensions limiting carriage on certain transports. 
* Volume: a numerical description of space limiting carriage to vessels which have enough total free space.

